===紐約尼克（2018–至今）===
2018年6月21日，紐約尼克在2018年NBA選秀大會中以第二輪第三十六順位選中了羅賓森<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nola.com/pelicans/index.ssf/2018/06/chalmette_mitchell_robinson_20.html|title=Former Chalmette star Mitchell Robinson goes to New York Knicks in NBA Draft 2018|work=NOLA.com|access-date=June 22, 2018}}</ref>。在參加2018年NBA夏季聯賽中，創下夏季聯賽蓋帽和進攻籃板的紀錄<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://hoopshype.com/2018/07/15/new-york-knicks-mitchell-robinson-summer-league-draft-steals/|title=Knicks' Mitchell Robinson had most blocks per game in summer league history|work=hoopshype.com|access-date=September 25, 2018}}</ref>。2018年7月8日，羅賓森與尼克隊正式簽約<ref>{{cite web |title=New York Knicks sign second-round draft pick Mitchell Robinson |url=https://www.nba.com/knicks/front-office-news/new-york-knicks-sign-second-round-draft-pick-mitchell-robinson |website=NBA.com |access-date=November 12, 2018 |date=July 8, 2018}}</ref>。

2021年2月12日，在對陣華盛頓奇才隊的第二節比賽中右手骨折，並在中場休息後沒有回到場上<ref>{{cite web |last1=Botte |first1=Peter |title=Mitchell Robinson fractures right hand in Knicks win |url=https://nypost.com/2021/02/12/mitchell-robinson-injures-hand-in-knicks-win-over-wizards/ |website=New York Post |access-date=February 19, 2021 |date=February 12, 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Selbe |first1=Nick |title=Knicks Center Mitchell Robinson Suffers Fractured Hand vs. Wizards, Will Undergo Surgery |url=https://www.si.com/nba/2021/02/13/knicks-center-mitchell-robinson-fractures-hand |website=Sports Illustrated |access-date=February 19, 2021 |date=February 13, 2021}}</ref>。3月22日，在與76人的比賽中復出。3月28日，與公鹿的第一節比賽中右腳骨折，賽季中第二次受傷。

==國家隊生涯==
在2017年，羅賓森入選美國U-19的國家隊名單，但未能入選最終參與[[U19世界青年籃球錦標賽|U19世界青年籃球錦標賽]]的12人名單<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bgdailynews.com/sports/wku/robinson-doesn-t-make-final-cut-for-usa-u-team/article_ab72d018-67c3-5b6f-b54b-da35b553ac46.html|title=Robinson doesn't make final cut for USA U19 team|last=News|first=the Daily|work=Bowling Green Daily News|access-date=July 6, 2017}}</ref>。

